{"tid":1443013,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔撚去北角","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:26:09.000Z","uid":116276,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0f2c52fc85c4a418051c7276e8533c3511ddfb","tid":1443013,"uid":116276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"唔撚去<br />\n<br />\n有手足踩咗線 一個星期觀察<br />\n<br />\n1. 沿海碼頭俾狗借哂 消防局碼頭都已經借出<br />\n<br />\n2. 西灣河水狗屋企增咗兵有100+備用狗隻<br />\n<br />\n3. 有兩大船快運30隻畜龍<br />\n<br />\n4. 最壞情況 手足一入北角打完 炮台山 鰂魚涌 沿海 三面有狗執死雞<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n<br />\n入咗北角不能夠全身而退<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n<br />\n西行 SSP 快閃港督<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會落場 各位手足自行判斷"},{"pid":"86f84282154148e610c1abdef3b974071c01001f","tid":1443013,"uid":18569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"話去個啲根本係送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f5610bd2c06e53d2451f25fc38c9addc99109e","tid":1443013,"uid":116276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚去"},{"pid":"1027696911fd0f37a3bd87e44007ba45f8dc4ae0","tid":1443013,"uid":116276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"唔撚去"},{"pid":"35f091cde88d5bb70b2c1b4da3730d1c647ff4d2","tid":1443013,"uid":116276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"唔撚去"},{"pid":"581928136bcd4949f38959433f83d170925ff62f","tid":1443013,"uid":116276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:13:54.000Z","msg":"唔撚去"},{"pid":"b11d3c5a771abca7b594cd7e248b23939e715ca6","tid":1443013,"uid":116276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"唔撚去"},{"pid":"972b6ecbd277f5a4bd554f442a72ce04c3b548de","tid":1443013,"uid":116276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"唔撚去"},{"pid":"a452cc75146672c215917e05a7